<div style="margin-top:40px;">
Atualmente, infelizmente, não ha um modo coveniente de instalar o gnuplot para o OS X mais novos, incluindo mountain lion. para instalar um gnuplot funcional devemos instalar  X11, zlib, libpng, freetype, e gdlib antes do proprio gnuplot
</div>

<h3>Instalar XQuartz</h3>

<p>
Download e instale <a href="http://xquartz.macosforge.org/landing/" title="http://xquartz.macosforge.org/landing/">XQuartz</a>.
</p>

<p></p>
<p>
Isso é necessario para ter um  <code>set terminal x11</code> (especificar um terminal)no Gnuplot, e habilita a rodar programas baseados em Xwindow 
</p>

<h3>Instale zlib</h3>

<p>
Faça o download  do source code para <a href="http://www.zlib.net" title="http://www.zlib.net">zlib</a>
 - abaixe até  zlib source code, versão 1.2.7, formato tar.gz
</p>

<p></p>
<p>
assumindo que você baixou e extraiu, abra um
<a href="http://www.apple.com/osx/apps/all.html#terminal" title="http://www.apple.com/osx/apps/all.html#terminal">Terminal window</a>, cd para a pasta do 
zlib source, configure, make, e install como segue:
</p>

<p></p>
<p>
</p><pre style="margin-left:4em">macuser:~/Downloads$ cd zlib-1.2.7
macuser:~/Downloads/zlib-1.2.7$ ./configure
macuser:~/Downloads/zlib-1.2.7$ make
macuser:~/Downloads/zlib-1.2.7$ sudo make install
</pre>
<p></p>

<h3>Instale libpng</h3>

<p>
Download e instale <a href="http://www.libpng.org/pub/png/libpng.html" title="http://www.libpng.org/pub/png/libpng.html">libpng</a>
</p>

<p></p>
<p>
</p><pre style="margin-left:4em">macuser:~/Downloads$ cd libpng-1.5.13
macuser:~/Downloads/libpng-1.5.13$ ./configure
macuser:~/Downloads/libpng-1.5.13$ make
macuser:~/Downloads/libpng-1.5.13$ make check
macuser:~/Downloads/libpng-1.5.13$ sudo make install
</pre>
<p></p>

<h3>Instale freetype</h3>

<p>
Download e instale  <a href="http://freetype.sourceforge.net/download.html#stable" title="http://freetype.sourceforge.net/download.html#stable">freetype</a>
Usando esse link:
<a href="http://download.savannah.gnu.org/releases/freetype/freetype-2.4.10.tar.gz" title="http://download.savannah.gnu.org/releases/freetype/freetype-2.4.10.tar.gz">http://download.savannah.gnu.org/releases/freetype/freetype-2.4.10.tar.gz</a>
</p>

<p></p>
<p>
</p><pre style="margin-left:4em">macuser:~/Downloads$ cd freetype-2.4.10
macuser:~/Downloads/freetype-2.4.10$ ./configure
macuser:~/Downloads/freetype-2.4.10$ make
macuser:~/Downloads/freetype-2.4.10$ sudo make install
</pre>
<p></p>

<h3>Instale libgd</h3>

<p>
Download e instale  <a href="http://www.boutell.com/gd/" title="http://www.boutell.com/gd/">libgd</a>
using this link:
<a href="http://www.boutell.com/gd/http/gd-2.0.33.tar.gz" title="http://www.boutell.com/gd/http/gd-2.0.33.tar.gz">http://www.boutell.com/gd/http/gd-2.0.33.tar.gz</a>
</p>

<p></p>
<p>
</p><pre style="margin-left:4em">macuser:~/Downloads$ cd gd-2.0.33
macuser:~/Downloads/gd-2.0.33$ ./configure
macuser:~/Downloads/gd-2.0.33$ make
macuser:~/Downloads/gd-2.0.33$ sudo make install
</pre>
<p></p>

<h3>Instale Gnuplot</h3>

<p>
Download e instale  <a href="http://sourceforge.net/projects/gnuplot/files/" title="http://sourceforge.net/projects/gnuplot/files/">Gnuplot</a>
</p>

<p></p>
<p>
Nota o <code>--with-readline=builtin</code> no arquivo de configuração -
o arquivo INSTALL explica o porque dele estar ai.
</p>

<p></p>
<p>
</p><pre style="margin-left:4em">macuser:~/Downloads$ cd gnuplot-4.6.0
macuser:~/Downloads/gnuplot-4.6.0$ ./configure --with-readline=builtin
macuser:~/Downloads/gnuplot-4.6.0$ make
macuser:~/Downloads/gnuplot-4.6.0$ sudo make install
</pre>
<p></p>

<p></p>
<p>
teste seu gnuplot usando um terminal:
</p>

<p></p>
<p>
</p><pre style="margin-left:4em">macuser:~ gnuplot
gnuplot&gt;  plot sin(x)

{% endblock %}
